These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, car, decembering
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, martial-arts, western, time-travel
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, italian, colombian, dutch
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, december, january, august
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person driving the boat##1
2. the dutch is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the colombian is the person watching fantasy movies##1
4. the person driving the decembering is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the turkish is on the left of the italian##1
7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who's birthday is in may##1
8. the italian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
9. the person driving the decembering is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Transport         | boat  | decembering  | jet-ski | car |
| Movie-Genre           | martial-arts | fantasy | time-travel  | western  |
| Nationality   | dutch       | colombian      | turkish | italian      |
| Birthday           | may          | december     | january    | august     |

