.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, indonesian, pakistani, spanish
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, whist, scrabble, snooker
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, begonia, daisy, lily
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, havana, fonseca, dannemann
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
2. the person who growslily is the montecristo-smoker##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the french##1
4. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the person playing whist##1
5. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
6. the pakistani is the person who growsdaisy##1
7. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the indonesian##1
8. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the french##1
9. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Nationality      | pakistani     | french       | indonesian | spanish        |
| Game          | snooker     | whist       | scrabble   | mah-jongg   |
| Flower   | daisy      | begonia       | lily     | balloon-flower    |
| Cigar         | fonseca | dannemann | montecristo | havana |

