.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, march, may, august
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, old-henry, game, swisher
City: colone, san-francisco, hamburg, marseilles
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, dubstep, r&b, hip-hop
 1. the person who's birthday is in august is the fan of hip-hop##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
 3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1
 4. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of country##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 6. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 7. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Birthday      | march | february       | august        | may        |
| Cigar           | old-henry   | game | blend   | swisher |
| City   | colone     | san-francisco    | marseilles | hamburg        |
| Music-Genre           | r&b         | country  | hip-hop       | dubstep         |

