.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, handball, ice-hockey, basketball
City: hannover, colone, marseilles, miami
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, car, van, train
4 different games are played: domino, go, snooker, whist
1. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person playing whist##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person playing domino##1
5. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
6. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
8. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
9. the person playing snooker is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Sport           | handball   | baseball  | basketball | ice-hockey |
| City   | marseilles | miami       | colone       | hannover     |
| Transport   | van       | train    | car     | trike  |
| Game           | go     | snooker | whist     | domino         |

