2. the person who likes black is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person who likes azure is on the far left##1
4. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
6. the person who likes orange is the person who growsdaisy##1
7. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
8. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
9. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage           | coffee  | tea    | fanta | sprite |
