.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
4 different games are played: chess, go, whist, bridge
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, azure, aquamarine, ivory
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, fonseca, vegafina, dunhill
House: farmhouse, wooden, townhouse, craftsman
 1. the person playing whist is the old-henry-smoker##1
 2. the person playing chess is the fonseca-smoker##1
 3. the person who likes brown is the old-henry-smoker##1
 4. the townhouse house is the person playing chess##1
 5. the vegafina-smoker is the person who likes ivory##1
 6. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing go##1
 7. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 8. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
 9. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left##1
10. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Game          | chess  | bridge | whist     | go |
| Color           | aquamarine  | ivory      | brown | azure    |
| Cigar   | fonseca | vegafina  | old-henry    | dunhill  |
| House           | townhouse   | craftsman       | farmhouse       | wooden      |

