.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-7::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, eggplant, cucumber, pear
4 different games are played: billiard, bridge, domino, whist
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, daisy, azalea, aconite
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, photographer, fisherman, doctor
 1. the person who growszinnia is the person playing bridge##1
 2. the doctor is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
 3. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 4. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person playing domino##1
 5. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 6. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 7. the person who growszinnia is the fisherman##1
 8. the person eating mango is on the far left##1
 9. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
10. the scientist is on the left of the fisherman##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Food    | mango | eggplant     | cucumber    | pear |
| Game       | billiard | domino    | whist | bridge |
| Flower         | daisy   | azalea  | aconite        | zinnia    |
| Job   | doctor   | photographer | scientist    | fisherman |

