4. the british is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
5. the fan of punk is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
6. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person playing go##1
7. the nigerian is the person playing go##1
8. the person playing domino is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
9. the person playing chess is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Hobby      | gardening      | video-games         | board-games        | magic-tricks      |
| Nationality           | nigerian | british | french  | argentine  |
