3. the futuristic house is on the far left##1
4. the wooden house is the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the palace house is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
6. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
7. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
8. the person watching disaster movies is the palace house##1
9. the person who likes red is on the right of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
| House      | futuristic     | palace           | ranch-style    | wooden    |
| Movie-Genre         | satire  | disaster | scientific  | superhero |
| Color   | azure     | red     | fuchsia | orange   |
