 4. the french is on the far right##1
 5. the person who likes azure is on the left of the italian##1
 6. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 7. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the italian##1
 8. the person driving the subway is on the left of the nigerian##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the italian##1
10. the person who likes apricot is the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3       |     4     |
| Color          | fuchsia  | azure   | apricot       | blood-red     |
| Pet         | horse | ferret | cat | goat     |
| Transport   | subway  | skateboard         | car       | airplane    |
| Nationality   | egyptian   | nigerian          | italian        | french |

